# Book API

## Overview
This API allows for CRUD operations on a Book model.

## Endpoints
- `GET /books/`: Retrieves a list of all books (public access).
- `GET /books/<int:pk>/`: Retrieves details of a specific book (public access).
- `POST /books/create/`: Creates a new book (authenticated users only).
- `PUT /books/<int:pk>/update/`: Updates an existing book (authenticated users only).
- `DELETE /books/<int:pk>/delete/`: Deletes a book (authenticated users only).

